     Pascal Hitzler, Marcus Krotzsch, Sebastion Rudolph
      Chapman and Hall Book(CRC Press)
[T2] Programming The Semantic Web
     Toby Segaran, Colin Evans, Jamie Taylor
      O’Reilly Media Publication

